The last date for applying online for financial assistance under the Snehapoorvam scheme being implemented through the Kerala Social Security Mission has been extended to January 15.Of the beneficiaries of the scheme, children of Class 10 and Plus Two who secured A+ in all subjects in 2014-15 will be given assistance for continuing their higher studies under the Snehapoorvam excellence scheme. The last date for applying online for the same has also been extended to January 15.â€“ Special Correspondent